1. composer.json
  "require-dev": {       
        "squizlabs/php_codesniffer": "3.*"
    },
2. setting composer(zero_webserver:latest) -> install->update.
  2.2 check /vendor/bin/phpcs and /vendor/bin/phpcbf
3. reboot phpstrom
4. settings->quality tool->code sniffer
5.  php code sniffer path -> /opt/project/vendor/bin/phpcs
6. enable code sniffer
